description:
Augusta Apartments where everyone wants to live!

Augusta is more than just apartments, it's a close-knit community of residents loving life in Seattle's fabulous famous U-District. Featuring a wide variety of 1-, 2-, and 3-bedroom floor plans, an abundance of amenities like a rooftop deck with water views, a state-of-the-art gym and basketball court, and an on-site reservable guest suite (great for graduation and Husky games), Augusta has everything you need to enhance your lifestyle.

You will love our prime location! Augusta is less than a 10-minute walk to University of Washington and rests in the heart of an iconic neighborhood rich with diverse restaurants (foodie heaven!), shops, pubs, and coffee houses. Augusta's appeal is a unique mix of external vibrancy and internal tranquility.

description:
AVA Capitol Hill features studio, 1 and 2 bedroom apartments. Now offering furnished and unfurnished apartments.

AVA Capitol Hill is steps away from bars, clubs, retail and all modes of transportation including easy access to I-5 Freeway, light rail, bus service and the new Capitol Hill Street Car. Now offering furnished and unfurnished apartments, AVA Capitol Hill features studio, 1 and 2 bedroom apartments with urban inspired design that extends beyond the walls to social spaces to connect, chill and play. Our Furnished+ homes come outfitted with essential stylish furniture plus all utilities, including cable and WiFi, are included in your rent. There is the roof deck for chilling and grilling under the lights of Seattle's skyline and lots of comfy seating for hanging out with friends. These Capitol Hill apartments are pet friendly and include an awesome fitness center.

description:
AVA Capitol Hill features studio, 1 and 2 bedroom apartments. Now offering furnished and unfurnished apartments.

AVA Capitol Hill is steps away from bars, clubs, retail and all modes of transportation including easy access to I-5 Freeway, light rail, bus service and the new Capitol Hill Street Car. Now offering furnished and unfurnished apartments, AVA Capitol Hill features studio, 1 and 2 bedroom apartments with urban inspired design that extends beyond the walls to social spaces to connect, chill and play. Our Furnished+ homes come outfitted with essential stylish furniture plus all utilities, including cable and WiFi, are included in your rent. There is the roof deck for chilling and grilling under the lights of Seattle's skyline and lots of comfy seating for hanging out with friends. These Capitol Hill apartments are pet friendly and include an awesome fitness center.

description: Discover comfortable, modern living at Jasper, where modern apartment living comes with a little more space in a welcoming, tree-lined neighborhood that already feels like home. Tucked away in North Seattle's Wedgwood community, Jasper is a retreat from urban life but still within a short trip to everything you love in the city. Enjoy a cup of coee on the rooftop deck or walk your dog in one of the area's many beautiful parks, then come back to a home that's as cozy as it is contemporary.

A variety of restaurants are just a five-minute walk away, including AQAU by El Gaucho, The Pink Door, Lola, Greenleaf Vietnamese Restaurant, Plaza Garibaldi, and Tilikum Place Café.

The IMAX Theater at the Pacific Science Center is only a five-minute walk away, and the Experience Music Project is only a few blocks further.
description:
AVA Belltown Apartments are situated in the heart of lively downtown Seattle and offer residents spectacular views of both Puget Sound and the Olympia Mountains. Now offering furnished and unfurnished apartments.

AVA Belltown Apartments are situated in the heart of lively downtown Seattle and offer residents spectacular views of both Puget Sound and the Olympia Mountains. These spacious Seattle apartments are ideal for individuals that prefer the perfect balance of nature and big city life. Now offering furnished and unfurnished apartments. Flexible leasing options are even available to suit the needs of current and potential tenants. As a result, whether you are planning on staying for a year or a decade, AVA Belltown is the perfect place to accommodate your time in Seattle. Our Belltown apartments offer spacious living with a long list of features that come standard in each apartment. The kitchens are stylish in design and have sleek hardwood floors with contrasting black appliances. A washer and dryer also come standard in each apartment and help tenants avoid late night runs to the Laundromat. Kitchens also come fully equipped with a microwave and dishwasher, which allows residents to feel right at home as soon as they move in. Our Furnished+ homes come outfitted with essential stylish furniture plus all utilities, including cable and WiFi, are included in your rent.

AVA Belltown Apartments are situated in the heart of lively downtown Seattle and offer residents spectacular views of both Puget Sound and the Olympia Mountains. Now offering furnished and unfurnished apartments.

AVA Belltown Apartments are situated in the heart of lively downtown Seattle and offer residents spectacular views of both Puget Sound and the Olympia Mountains. These spacious Seattle apartments are ideal for individuals that prefer the perfect balance of nature and big city life. Now offering furnished and unfurnished apartments. Flexible leasing options are even available to suit the needs of current and potential tenants. As a result, whether you are planning on staying for a year or a decade, AVA Belltown is the perfect place to accommodate your time in Seattle. Our Belltown apartments offer spacious living with a long list of features that come standard in each apartment. The kitchens are stylish in design and have sleek hardwood floors with contrasting black appliances. A washer and dryer also come standard in each apartment and help tenants avoid late night runs to the Laundromat. Kitchens also come fully equipped with a microwave and dishwasher, which allows residents to feel right at home as soon as they move in. Our Furnished+ homes come outfitted with essential stylish furniture plus all utilities, including cable and WiFi, are included in your rent.

description:
The Cove is an award winning, LEED Platinum community right in the heart of Capitol Hill. Each of our pet-friendly homes comes equipped with programmable A/C units; full-size, front-load washers and dryers; as well as spacious kitchens with energy efficient stainless steel appliances including full- and XL-sized fridges/freezers and full-sized dishwashers. Lofty ceilings open up your living space allowing sunlight to stream in through over-sized floor-to-ceiling windows.

The Cove's excellent location makes it easy to navigate the city in any direction. Both downtown Seattle and Capitol Hill's light rail station are only 10 minute walks, and Microsoft's Connector Bus stop is only a block away. Proximity to major grocery stores including Whole Foods, QFC, and Amazon's novel Amazon Go Grocery make car-free living easy!

Enjoy breathtaking views of Lake Union, the cityscape and the Space Needle from your private deck or the rooftop terrace. Residents enjoy electric vehicle chargers, a landscaped courtyard with water features, outdoor fire features and nearby running paths. Modern, work from home-friendly amenities include a business center, conference room and media center. We are located in the service area of Comcast Fiber Internet, within walking distance to Facebook and driving distance to Amazon, Google and the University of Washington. We accept a variety of sources of income.

description: The Whittaker's location in the Junction makes it easy to access parks, beach, water and recreation. When you're ready to start exploring, West Seattle's natural green paradise won't disappoint. Whether you're jogging on the paved Alki Beach path, playing volleyball in the sand nearby, or hiking the area's off-road trails, you can freely indulge your wanderlust. Any thrilling day can be capped off with a dip in Lincoln Park's heated saltwater pool for the ultimate refreshment of body and mind. West Seattle is also home to many great restaurants, shops and entertainment. The West Seattle Junction at California Avenue and Alaska Street offers plenty of opportunities for unforgettable dining experiences, local flavor, and unique gifts. For those itching for even more, The Whittaker is mere minutes away from numerous bus, bike and water taxi routes and a short ride to the Sea-Tac airport to get you to your next adventure.

description:
When it's time to select the songs that make up the soundtrack to your life, you want to create the perfect playlist. Choosing a new luxury apartment on Capitol Hill in Seattle is like choosing the cover art for your next album. Located in the heart of Capitol Hill at Broadway and East John, and just minutes from downtown Seattle, The Lyric puts you in the middle of the area's most prominent nightlife and entertainment district. Take advantage of all Capitol Hill has to offer simply by walking out your door, or play a mellow tune and relax in your new home while enjoying sweeping views of Mt. Rainier and the Seattle skyline.

 

The Lyric offers luxurious amenities that will be music to your ears with 234 uniquely designed Studio, One and Two bedroom apartment homes. The Lyric offers a state of the art fitness center, high tech theatre and gaming room, a resident sky lounge, underground parking and a private courtyard.

description:
Join the diverse, innovative and welcoming community at Othello Square. As part of a larger, long-anticipated neighborhood development, Orenda adds 176 affordable and market rate apartment homes to the project's schools, medical services, multicultural center and more. The final, four-building campus is being designed as an economic and cultural anchor for the Rainier Valley.

Orenda offers studio, one-, two-, and three-bedroom layout options with high ceilings, unique design, quality finishes and the latest in-demand amenities.

Come home to modern living right on Seattle's Light Rail route, where rooftop views, amazing dining from around the world and the rest of the city are all only steps away.
